  ('Coach Call-Out Ladder Pattern', 'coach-call-out-ladder-pattern', 'Coach Call-Out Ladder Pattern is a ladder-focused exercise for listen, choose the correct pattern, and move crisply without guessing.', 'INTERMEDIATE', 8, 2, 2, 15, 30, 55, 'individual', 'Coach Call-Out Ladder Pattern uses the ladder to build listen, choose the correct pattern, and move crisply without guessing. Best used as a crisp, low-volume skill or power exposure rather than a fatigue circuit.', 'Primary phase: Movement Intelligence. Subrole: perception_action_reactive_movement. Treat the ladder as a constraint for precision; progress speed only after clean rhythm, posture, and spacing.', 'Fast feet are only good if they are clean feet.', 'Reactive ladder decision', 'movement_intelligence', 'perception_action_reactive_movement', 'ladder_reactive_decision', '{"primary_joint_actions":["ankle_dorsiflexion","hip_flexion_extension","knee_drive","trunk_upright_posture"],"primary_tissues":["plantar_foot","calves","hip_flexors","glutes"],"breathing_demand":"natural rhythmic breathing","balance_demand":"dynamic balance over changing foot positions","coordination_demand":"rapid foot placement, rhythm, and spatial awareness","impact_level":1,"reactive_output_profile":{"stimulus_type":"coach, partner, color, number, or ball cue","decision_count":"1-3 options based on athlete level","amplitude_cap":"short ladder pass only; no fatigue chase"}}'::jsonb, '{"movement_description":"Coach Call-Out Ladder Pattern uses the agility ladder as a visual target to train listen, choose the correct pattern, and move crisply without guessing. The athlete moves through the boxes with clean contacts, controlled posture, and enough rest to keep every rep crisp.","setup":["Lay the agility ladder flat and remove tripping hazards.","Show one slow walk-through rep before speed is allowed.","Start tall with eyes forward, arms ready, and feet just outside the first box."],"execution_steps":["Step through the ladder using the assi